Address key normalization:

```
{ ... }        ->  { ... }
"10.0.0.1/24"  ->  {"address": "10.0.0.1",
                    "prefixlen": 24}
```

Interface key normalization:

```
{ ... }  ->  { ... }
"eth0"   ->  {"ifname": "eth0", ...}
1        ->  {"index": 1, ...}
```

